11 connection with nonresidential real estate, of the clock hours required under paragraph (1)
12 of this subsection, 2 clock hours shall be satisfied by a course regarding the federal
13 Americans with Disabilities Act.
14 (3) A licensee holding a license from another state must complete at least
15 the number of clock hours of continuing education instruction required under paragraph
