20 (ii) the Real Estate Brokers of Baltimore, Inc.;
21 (iii) any similar professional association; or
22 (iv) an educational institution approved by the Commission.
23 (2) Notwithstanding any other provision of law, continuing education
24 courses shall be taught by a qualified instructor who is experienced in the real estate
25 industry and selected by the course provider.
